description:
The VerificationPipeline currently does not validate that requested strategies are properly implemented. Placeholder strategies (that return QAInterrogator) silently produce incorrect results.

Recommendation: Add validation in pipeline initialization or verify_components():

def _validate_strategies(self) -> None:
    for st in self._config.enabled_strategies:
        strategy = self._registry.get(st)
        if strategy.strategy_type != st:
            raise ValueError(f'Strategy {st} returns wrong type (placeholder)')

This would fail fast rather than produce misleading scores.

